\title{Bayesian Tuning for Binary Boosted Tree Models}
\description{
Performance-oriented Bayesian hyperparameter tuning for binary boosted tree models with parsnip-style boost-tree parameter names, cached cross-validation, Limbo ask/tell optimization, automatic parallel controls, class-imbalance handling, and optional native PR-AUC scoring backends.
}
